How to use the scripts.

$ wget http://ww1.microchip.com/downloads/en/softwarelibrary/microchip-libraries-for-applications-v2013-06-15-windows-installer.exe

$ chmod +x microchip-libraries-for-applications-v2013-06-15-windows-installer.exe

$ ./microchip-libraries-for-applications-v2013-06-15-windows-installer.exe

...
install library wherewer you want
...

$ cd microchip_solutions_v2013-06-15
$ moralizer
$ patch -t -p2 < microchip_solutions_v2013-06-15.patch
$ cd USB/Device_-_HID_-_Mouse/Firmware/
$ ln -s ~/Makefile
$ make all
$ vim preproc/mouse.c		press Ctrl-h at symbol you want to display in preview window

